<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 15:14:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如果中国限制进口，欧盟猪肉行业将面临“噩梦”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-pork-industry-faces-nightmare-if-china-restricts-imports-2024-06-14/</link><description>行业高管和分析师周五表示，如果中国限制从该地区的进口，欧洲猪肉行业将面临价格下跌和利润下降的“噩梦”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-pork-industry-faces-nightmare-if-china-restricts-imports-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>上海允许特斯拉开展全自动驾驶试点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shanghai-allows-tesla-carry-out-full-self-driving-pilot-2024-06-14/</link><description>据当地政府支持的《上海观察家报》周五报道，上海将允许 10 辆特斯拉汽车对该公司最先进的自动驾驶软件进行测试，为其在中国的推出铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 13:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shanghai-allows-tesla-carry-out-full-self-driving-pilot-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>德拉吉表示，欧盟需要更便宜的能源和更好的产业政策来竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-needs-cheaper-energy-better-industrial-policy-compete-draghi-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>意大利前总理马里奥·德拉吉在欧盟委托发布的报告之前表示，欧洲必须降低能源价格，发展资本市场，并制定更强有力的工业和贸易政策，以保持竞争力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 13:18:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-needs-cheaper-energy-better-industrial-policy-compete-draghi-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称七国集团领导人讨论采取更多措施为中国提供公平竞争环境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-leaders-discuss-more-steps-level-china-playing-field-us-official-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>一位美国高级官员周五表示，七国集团（G7）领导人正在讨论采取更多措施，以平衡与中国的贸易竞争环境并保护其经济安全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 12:52:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-leaders-discuss-more-steps-level-china-playing-field-us-official-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，宝马电动 Mini 面临欧盟最高电动汽车关税威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-electric-mini-threatened-with-highest-ev-tariff-eu-source-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>一位知情人士周五表示，根据欧盟的临时计划，宝马在中国制造的全电动Mini将受到最高38.1%的电动汽车关税的打击，这对这款中档汽车的销售前景可能是致命一击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 12:51:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-electric-mini-threatened-with-highest-ev-tariff-eu-source-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>印度拉贾斯坦邦开始召回部分批次MDH、珠穆朗玛峰香料</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-rajasthan-starts-recalling-some-batches-mdh-everest-spices-2024-06-14/</link><description>印度西部拉贾斯坦邦已开始召回一些批次的流行 MDH 和 Everest 香料，这些香料被发现食用不安全，一位高级官员表示，这是国内和全球对这些品牌日益严格审查的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-rajasthan-starts-recalling-some-batches-mdh-everest-spices-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军事首长敦促渔民无视中国海警新规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-chief-urges-fishermen-ignore-chinas-new-coastguard-rules-2024-06-14/</link><description>菲律宾军事首长敦促菲律宾渔民继续在该国南海专属经济区捕鱼，尽管中国海警新规定允许其不经审判拘留非法侵入者，该规定于6月15日生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:42:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-chief-urges-fishermen-ignore-chinas-new-coastguard-rules-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国可能对欧盟企业征收电动汽车关税进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-potential-probes-eu-firms-following-ev-tariffs-2024-06-14/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国企业已要求政府对从欧盟进口的猪肉发起反倾销调查，并对欧盟乳制品发起反补贴调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:35:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-potential-probes-eu-firms-following-ev-tariffs-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团警告伊朗核计划持续升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-warns-iran-over-continuing-nuclear-programme-escalation-2024-06-14/</link><description>根据公报草案，七国集团领导人周五警告伊朗不要推进其核浓缩计划，并表示，如果德黑兰向俄罗斯转让弹道导弹，他们将准备实施新措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:19:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-warns-iran-over-continuing-nuclear-programme-escalation-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：消费者检查，但不要忘记法国和日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-14/</link><description>Alun John 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于需求波动，中国 5 月份新增银行贷款增幅远低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-new-bank-loans-rise-far-less-than-expected-may-2024-06-14/</link><description>中国5月份新增银行贷款的反弹远低于预期，一些关键货币指标创下历史新低，这表明尽管央行试图提振信心，但世界第二大经济体仍在努力重新站稳脚跟。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-new-bank-loans-rise-far-less-than-expected-may-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡门将呼吁中国球迷停止给他寄钱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/singapore-goalkeeper-urges-chinese-fans-stop-sending-him-money-2024-06-14/</link><description>新加坡国家队门将哈桑·桑尼在新加坡1-3输给泰国的比赛中做出扑救，帮助中国队晋级世界杯预选赛下一轮，他敦促中国球迷停止给他寄钱。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:48:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/singapore-goalkeeper-urges-chinese-fans-stop-sending-him-money-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>印度表示对电动汽车征收高关税是为了防止中国进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/india-says-high-tariffs-evs-protect-chinese-imports-2024-06-14/</link><description>印度贸易部门周五表示，在欧盟等其他主要经济体对中国电动汽车征收关税之际，该国的汽车市场通过对电动汽车进口征收高关税而“得到了很好的保护”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/india-says-high-tariffs-evs-protect-chinese-imports-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构称特斯拉将修复中国 5,836 辆进口汽车的软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-5836-imported-cars-china-watchdog-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>中国市场监管机构周五表示，特斯拉将以安全问题为由，将从 7 月起修复 5,836 辆进口 Model 3、Model S 和 Model X 汽车的软件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-5836-imported-cars-china-watchdog-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>德国表示中国需要在电动汽车关税争端中采取“认真行动”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/germany-trying-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-bloomberg-news-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>德国希望中国在进口电动汽车关税问题上采取“严肃行动”，并希望未来几周的谈判能够避免不断升级的贸易冲突，交通部长周五警告称，贸易冲突可能是灾难性的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/germany-trying-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-bloomberg-news-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>